text.section:
All licenses under KRS 243.020 to 243.670 shall be in such form as may be prescribed by regulations of the board and shall contain:
The name and address of the licensee;
The number of the license;
The type of the license;
A description by street and number, or otherwise, of the licensed premises;
The name and address of the owner of the building in which the licensed premises are located;
The expiration date of the license;
A statement in substance that the license shall not be a property or vested right and that it may be revoked at any time pursuant to law.
